Interface LoaderRoutine<IN,OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    IN - the input data type.
    OUT - the output data type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Routine<IN,OUT>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LoaderRoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>

    public interface LoaderRoutine<IN,OUT>
extends Routine<IN,OUT>
    Interface defining a routine that can clear specific invocation instances, identifying them by their inputs.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 03/09/2015.
